<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    {# Title #}
    <title>Inscription - Le blog de Jean Dupont</title>

    {# Google font #}
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Merienda:wght@300..900&family=Satisfy&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    {# SEO #}
    <meta name="robots" content="index, allow">
    <meta name="description" content="Inscrivez-vous pour lire des articles perninents sur la santé">
    <meta name="keywords" content="santé, médécine, inscription, Jean Dupont">
    <meta name="author" content="bastille">
    <meta name="publisher" content="bastille">

    {# CSS part of Bootstrap 5 #}
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">

    {# My stylesheet #}
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.css">

</head>
<body>

    {% for flash_error in app.flashes('verify_email_error') %}
        <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">{{ flash_error }}</div>
    {% endfor %}

    <div class="container my-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-7 text-center">
                {# Image #}
                <img src="/images/visitor/registration/Inscrivez-vous-pour-lire-des-articles-sur-la-sante.png" alt="Inscrivez vous pour lire des articles sur la sante" class="img-fluid">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-5">
                {# Formulaire #}
                {{form_start(registrationForm)}}
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="mb-3 col-md-6">
                            <label for="registration_form_firstName">Prénom</label>
                            <div class="text-danger">{{form_errors(registrationForm.firstName)}}</div>
                            {{form_widget(registrationForm.firstName, {'attr': {'class':'form-control', 'autofocus':'autofocus'}})}}
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3 col-md-6">
                            <label for="registration_form_lastName">Nom</label>
                             <div class="text-danger">{{form_errors(registrationForm.lastName)}}</div>
                            {{form_widget(registrationForm.lastName, {'attr': {'class':'form-control'}})}}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="registration_form_email">Email</label>
                         <div class="text-danger">{{form_errors(registrationForm.email)}}</div>
                        {{form_widget(registrationForm.email, {'attr': {'class':'form-control'}})}}
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="registration_form_password_first">Mot de pass</label>
                         <div class="text-danger">{{form_errors(registrationForm.password.first)}}</div>
                        {{form_widget(registrationForm.password.first, {'attr': {'class':'form-control', 'placeholder':'Au moins 12 caractères'}})}}
                        <small><em>Le mot de pass doit contenir au mois une lettre majuscule, minuscule, un chiffre et un caractère spécial.</em></small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="registration_form_password_second">Confirmation du mot de pass</label>
                         <div class="text-danger">{{form_errors(registrationForm.password.second)}}</div>
                        {{form_widget(registrationForm.password.second, {'attr': {'class':'form-control', 'placeholder':'Au moins 12 caractères'}})}}
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                       {{form_widget(registrationForm.agreeTerms)}}
                       <label for="registration_form_agreeTerms">Lire et accepter <a href="#" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#staticBackdrop">les conditions générales d'utilisation</a>
                       </label>
                        <!-- Modal -->
                        <div class="modal fade" id="staticBackdrop" data-bs-backdrop="static" data-bs-keyboard="false" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="staticBackdropLabel" aria-hidden="true">
                            <div class="modal-dialog">
                                <div class="modal-content">
                                    <div class="modal-header">
                                        <h2 class="modal-title fs-5" id="exampleModalLabel">Les conditions générales d'utilisation</h2>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="modal-body">
                                        <p>Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Est repellendus quis, dolorem ex cumque necessitatibus? Fuga pariatur quis et ipsam deserunt sint sed. Fuga ab esse dolor ea tempora voluptatibus, modi iste perspiciatis, odit repellendus error. Vel, libero sequi, possimus tempora nemo illum modi ipsum facere quisquam, quos neque veritatis.</p>
                                        <p>Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Est repellendus quis, dolorem ex cumque necessitatibus? Fuga pariatur quis et ipsam deserunt sint sed. Fuga ab esse dolor ea tempora voluptatibus, modi iste perspiciatis, odit repellendus error. Vel, libero sequi, possimus tempora nemo illum modi ipsum facere quisquam, quos neque veritatis.</p>
                                        <p>Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Est repellendus quis, dolorem ex cumque necessitatibus? Fuga pariatur quis et ipsam deserunt sint sed. Fuga ab esse dolor ea tempora voluptatibus, modi iste perspiciatis, odit repellendus error. Vel, libero sequi, possimus tempora nemo illum modi ipsum facere quisquam, quos neque veritatis.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="modal-footer">
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Fermer</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <input formnovalidate type="submit" class="btn btn-primary shadow w-100" value="S'inscrire">
                    </div>
                {{form_end(registrationForm)}}
                <div class="my-3 text-center">
                    <p>
                        Vous avez déjà un compte? 
                        <a href="{{path('visitor_authentication_login')}}">Connectez-vous</a>
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <a href="{{path('visitor_welcome_index')}}">Retour à l'accueil</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {# JS part of Bootstrap 5 #}
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
